Implemented AR overlay rendering with label positioning: ARLabelPositioner (positioning/scaling logic), AROverlayView (renders POI labels with animation), integrated into ContentView. Features: 45° horizontal FOV arc centered on heading, labels with name + downward arrow, distance-based vertical positioning (closer=lower+larger, farther=higher+smaller), smooth continuous scaling, label sliding in/out on device turn, partial clipping at edges, real-time orientation updates, active distance range filtering (100m-50km). Comprehensive test suite: 43 tests for positioning logic (FOV, distance, bearing, scaling, clipping, opacity), 4 tests for overlay views, 4 integration tests. All tests validate happy path and edge cases (bearing wrap-around at 0/360°, FOV boundaries, screen bounds). Ready for Xcode build.
